{"Sid":0,"Did":118410,"Id":"282937","Title":"日月宮","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/da1644cb-4c11-4813-a79d-a0fbab952361/collection/6e515a2a-c1eb-45f3-b7d5-a80d39f552bc/108-sea-pa-1793-201910281851115db6a44c40a4e0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n日月宮位於宜蘭縣蘇澳鎮金字山，主祀太陽星君和太陰神君，是全台灣少有的供奉日月二神的道教廟宇之一。 日月宮由道號鼎陽法師的劉祥臨發起創立，年輕拜師求學的鼎陽法師平生敬仰日月星君，習得混元之理，修行有道，因此於1965年開始興建，起初落成的日月宮只有簡陋的鐵皮屋。後來隨著神威顯赫而香火日益旺盛，信眾人數絡繹往來增加，於1968年日月宮開始籌備第一次擴建，再經1985年再次平基興建擴蓋，如今的日月宮太陽公廟增添祀奉鬼谷先師、福德正神、中壇元帥、玉皇上帝與九天玄女，是蘇澳鎮規模宏大的重要道教廟宇。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.8511592","Keyword_Latitude":"24.5920458","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/BC08A775-5763-4188-8052-B619B16CF020","Original_Identifier":"282937","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"宗教場所 / 道教 / 蘇澳","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 00:45:43","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣蘇澳鎮永光里永光路50巷5號","longitude":"121.8511592","latitude":"24.5920458","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"莊文生;鄭文嵐;高璇","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/da1644cb-4c11-4813-a79d-a0fbab952361/collectionOpen/d6292d86-dcff-4da1-ac18-3eed56794c45/108-sea-pa-1793-re-201910281852365db6a44c40a4e0.jpg"}}